<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>永旺</title><link>https://aeon.co/feed.atom</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 12:18:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>神秘的园艺艺术</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/a-rebel-spirit-and-an-artists-eye-russell-pages-landscape-design?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="两座狮身人面像般的雕像前景是一个复杂的正式花园，花园里有几何树篱和一个方形池塘。背景是盛开的樱花树" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/0eb69a89-5f85-4594-a982-04a8c93d4ceb/header_essay-v1-blossom.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;在 20 世纪郊区扩张的时代，伟大的设计师拉塞尔·佩奇 (Russell Page) 将深情的哲学注入他的花园&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——凯莱布·史密斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/a-rebel-spirit-and-an-artists-eye-russell-pages-landscape-design?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/a-rebel-spirit-and-an-artists-eye-russell-pages-landscape-design?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>细胞世界</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/explore-a-bioluminescent-world-of-cellular-life-via-cutting-edge-microscopy?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/b1212f79-d7c0-43b7-af91-970638d6d2af/header_cell-worlds-landscape-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;科学技术与艺术的融合，带来一场令人眼花缭乱的“隐藏在我们每个人心中”的微观星系之旅&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/explore-a-bioluminescent-world-of-cellular-life-via-cutting-edge-microscopy?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/explore-a-bioluminescent-world-of-cellular-life-via-cutting-edge-microscopy?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>你是艺术天才吗？</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/you-can-be-truly-creative-if-you-let-go-of-your-assumptions?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/d6b37363-a465-4579-8cc5-cf1ba3e16207/header_essay-gettyimages-1315366028.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;也许不是，但如果这是你在生活中发挥创造力的门槛，那么你就完全错了&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——詹姆斯·C·考夫曼&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/you-can-be-truly-creative-if-you-let-go-of-your-assumptions?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/you-can-be-truly-creative-if-you-let-go-of-your-assumptions?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>保罗·菲佛：中断广播</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/a-unique-project-frames-college-football-as-an-intricately-choreographed-mass-ritual?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/3ee60bba-1e91-4b2e-85aa-a1d2375a253f/header_paul-pfeiffer-interrupting-the-broadcast-landscape-4.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;现场体育赛事的巧妙制作如何操纵观众的情绪，创造近乎宗教的体验&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/a-unique-project-frames-college-football-as-an-intricately-choreographed-mass-ritual?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/a-unique-project-frames-college-football-as-an-intricately-choreographed-mass-ritual?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>最后的道德边界</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/as-space-gets-more-commercial-how-can-it-be-governed-ethically?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="玻璃穹顶下的人物观看火箭从火星表面发射" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/cb72851c-2cd7-4df9-bdc1-11b30a81fbc7/header_essay-spacex-on-mars-qalnmz8hsnj8zuggdpiftj.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;地球探索受到殖民主义、剥削和榨取的困扰。我们能希望让空间变得不同吗？&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——菲利普·鲍尔&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/as-space-gets-more-commercial-how-can-it-be-governed-ethically?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/as-space-gets-more-commercial-how-can-it-be-governed-ethically?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>欧文·芬克尔的古代恶魔</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-absentee-gods-and-nefarious-spirits-of-ancient-mesopotamia?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/916e16b0-51bd-473b-9900-c3e47be6d91a/header_ancient-demons-with-irving-finkel-landscape-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;有趣的亚述学家欧文·芬克尔解开了古代美索不达米亚缺席的诸神和爱管闲事的灵魂的网络&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-absentee-gods-and-nefarious-spirits-of-ancient-mesopotamia?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/meet-the-absentee-gods-and-nefarious-spirits-of-ancient-mesopotamia?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>已经看过</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/deja-vu-a-window-on-the-past-and-a-key-to-human-survival?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="床上放着一顶巴拿马帽，午后的阳光透过纱帘照射进来。有轻微的运动模糊" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/bed33711-15d1-4efb-9558-a206aab8b454/header_test-nn11556269.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;你有没有来过这里？那种怪异的感觉是你的心灵在向内寻找自己生存的线索的影子&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——安妮·克利里&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/deja-vu-a-window-on-the-past-and-a-key-to-human-survival?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/deja-vu-a-window-on-the-past-and-a-key-to-human-survival?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>与相对主义的斗争</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/86d431d8-d3cd-4891-8f6b-aabd112c5c66/header_essay-goya-6985.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;伯纳德·威廉姆斯认为，一个人的道德是由文化和历史塑造的。但这并不意味着每个人都是对的&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——丹尼尔·卡尔卡特&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/bernard-williams-moral-relativism-and-the-culture-wars?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>房间</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/against-her-fathers-warnings-debra-resolves-to-learn-about-his-time-in-auschwitz?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/335f55d2-5a3c-4c26-b174-edbbe6a9fca7/header_the-room-landscape-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;濒临死亡的父亲向女儿讲述了他在奥斯威辛集中营的经历。他的故事成为她无法离开的房间&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/against-her-fathers-warnings-debra-resolves-to-learn-about-his-time-in-auschwitz?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/against-her-fathers-warnings-debra-resolves-to-learn-about-his-time-in-auschwitz?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item><item><title>一场破坏社会的考试</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/why-chinese-minds-still-bear-the-long-shadow-of-keju?utm_source=atom-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="许多身着传统服饰的人物聚集在一个悬挂着纸质清单的结构下方。前景是马。颜色随着年龄的增长而变得柔和" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/4e582db8-120d-48e8-bcfb-f718d171bc95/header_essay-ming-beamtenprufungen1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;科举是中国极其困难的公务员考试，它以自由和创造力为代价强化了国家力量&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——黄亚生&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/why-chinese-minds-still-bear-the-long-shadow-of-keju?utm_source=atom-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/why-chinese-minds-still-bear-the-long-shadow-of-keju?utm_source=atom-feed</guid></item></channel></rss>